   "source": [
    "## KALLISTO"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**1) Install it with conda by running:**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "conda install -c bioconda kallisto "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**2) Set a working directory**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cd '/Users/jnz16/PhD/InVivo/Seq/Analysis/Kallisto_Ailsa' "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**3) Create index with Kallisto and the fasta file downloaded from Ensembl**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "kallisto index -i Homo_sapiens.GRCh37.cdna.all.fa "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "kallisto quant --index=kallist_human_index --output-dir='/Users/jnz16//PhD/InVivo/Seq/Analysis/Kallisto_Ailsa' "
   ]
  }
